# Rule Drawer (Shared)

Used by Earning and Redemption rule modules. Side panel for create/edit; fields change by `RuleType`.

## Layout

- **Default:** Right-side drawer (`max-w-xl`) with dimmed backdrop; backdrop click closes.
- **Full screen:** Header **Expand** (`Expand01`) toggles to full viewport; backdrop hidden; form content uses `max-w-6xl` centered grid. **Exit full screen** (`Minimize01`) restores side panel. State resets when drawer closes.

## Base fields (all types)

- Rule name, Rule code
- **Rule period** — `DateRangeField` (`src/components/DateRangeField.tsx`), `periodStart`/`periodEnd`, synced on drawer open
- Rule type selector

## Redemption-only fields

Cap type, value point %, value min, value max

## Conditional fields by rule type

| Rule Type | Key fields |
|-----------|------------|
| `activity` | Activity type, amount field, receive/redeem point |
| `third_party_points` | Card type multi-select; repeatable Partner Earning Blocks (tier table + per-block caps) — ARCH §4.4.1 |
| `personal_earning` | Type (birthday), target user CSV, reward type, receive point |
| `transactional` | Source system, transaction type (gated by source — Saving: Purchase/Payment; Cardlink: TC 40), merchant, card, channel, amount, conversion unit, multiplier, caps |
| `tactical` | Campaign name, target user, reward type + all transactional fields |

## Point calculation

`calculatePoints()` in `src/utils/points.ts`:

```
floor((transactionAmount / conversionUnit) × multiplier)
Example: (500,000 / 100,000) × 10 = 50 poin
```

## Actions

| Action | Add | Edit | Persistence |
|--------|-----|------|-------------|
| Cancel | ✓ | ✓ | — |
| Expand / Exit full screen | ✓ | ✓ | — |
| Submit for review / Save changes | ✓ | ✓ | Non-functional |

## Rule lifecycle

`draft` → `in_review` (Submit) → `scheduled` (Approve) → `active` (GoLive) → `inactive` | `expired`

Guards in `src/domain/ruleStatus.ts`, workflow stubs in `src/services/ruleWorkflow.ts`.
